OL,3,CPatient ratings may be used by NHS to
OL,4,Cdecide whether hospitals receive
OL,5,Cfunding
OL,7,FPatient ratings could be used to
OL,8,Fdecide how much funding hospitals get
OL,9,Fas part of plans to overhaul the NHS,
OL,10,FITV News understands.
OL,12,FThe changes may also see a bonus
OL,13,Fsystem introduced, with rewards for
OL,14,Fhospital bosses and staff who make
OL,15,Fprogress in tackling waiting times and
OL,16,Fimprove struggling trusts.
OL,18,FIt comes as Prime Minister Sir Keir
OL,19,FStarmer is set to outline a ten-year
OL,20,Fhealth plan to streamline the NHS and
OL,21,Framp up efficiency.
