OL,7,FITV News understands the patient
OL,8,Frating system is currently a proposal,
OL,9,Fand would involve a trial and NHS
OL,10,Fconsultation before it is implemented.
OL,12,FSeveral weeks after being treated in
OL,13,Fhospital, patients would be asked to
OL,14,Frate the care they received.
