OL,3,CPatient ratings may be used by NHS to
OL,4,Cdecide whether hospitals receive
OL,5,Cfunding
OL,7,FPositive reviews would lead to
OL,8,Fhospitals receiving the full funding -
OL,9,Fbut if patients felt their care wasn't
OL,10,Fup to standard, the money would go to
OL,11,Fa central NHS improvement fund
OL,12,Finstead. The approach would try to
OL,13,Fincentivise hospitals to listen to
OL,14,Fpatients' needs.
OL,16,FThe introduction of pay rewards would
OL,17,Fbe a first in the NHS, and would see
OL,18,Fsalaries linked to hospital
OL,19,Fperformance.
