OL,7,FIt comes after Health Secretary Wes
OL,8,FStreeting lamented health inequalities
OL,9,Fin an interview with ITV News on
OL,10,FWednesday, where he vowed to tackle
OL,11,Fthe disparity between services.
OL,13,FHe said: "The gap between the rich and
OL,14,Fpoor, between good and bad services is
OL,15,Fstark."
OL,17,FThe government's ten-year plan will be
OL,18,Funveiled next week.
